# Playwright Page Object Model (this repo)

Global default for all Cursor chats: **`~/.cursor/rules/playwright-page-object-model.mdc`** (`alwaysApply: true`). Follow that rule here.

## Repo layout

- **`src/page/BasePage.ts`** — `page`, shared **`body`** locator, `open()`, URL/assert helpers.
- Feature surfaces extend **`BasePage`**, implement **`rootPath()`**, own **class-scoped locators** and **`private static readonly`** selector/pattern constants.

## Locators

- **`readonly` fields at class scope**: `private readonly saveBtn = this.page.getByRole(...)`.
- **Constants at class scope**: `private static readonly FOO_SELECTOR = '...'` / regex patterns; instance locator fields reference them.
- No locator assembly in **constructors** beyond **`super(page)`** and storing injected values (e.g. conversation path).
- Prefer **named private methods** for post-condition assertions over inline closures inside flows (`assertConversationThreadOpened`, etc.).

## Tests

- Consume pages via **`tests/fixtures.ts`** (`customizationPage`, `inboxPage`, `conversationDetailPage`, …); avoid duplicating selectors in specs.
